OL,3,CAbuser's early release blocked after
OL,4,Cex-wife exposes MoJ admin error
OL,6,FA woman has successfully blocked moves
OL,7,Fto grant her ex-husband early release
OL,8,Ffrom prison after exposing a major
OL,9,Ferror in legal documents.
OL,11,FElizabeth Hudson was told last
OL,12,FSeptember that Martin Underwood, who
OL,13,Fhad repeatedly abused her during the
OL,14,Fcourse of their marriage, would be
OL,15,Ffreed under a new Government scheme to
OL,16,Fcurb overcrowding in prisons.
