OL,3,CAbuser's early release blocked after
OL,4,Cex-wife exposes MoJ admin error
OL,6,FThe 49-year-old ex-army sergeant had
OL,7,Fbeen given a six-year and three-month
OL,8,Fsentence after he attacked Ms Hudson
OL,9,Fat their home in Barnsley in April
OL,10,F2021 before assaulting another woman
OL,11,Fwhile on bail.
OL,13,FUnderwood was convicted of non-fatal
OL,14,Fstrangulation, an offence which should
OL,15,Fpreclude a prisoner from being
OL,16,Freleased early.
OL,18,FHowever, Ministry of Defence (MoJ)
OL,19,Frecords showed he was jailed for the
OL,20,Flesser offence of assault occasioning
OL,21,Factual bodily harm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
