OL,6,FMs Hudson raised the issue with the
OL,7,FMoJ, but it was only after official
OL,8,Fcourt documents were obtained by a
OL,9,Fjournalist that the early release was
OL,10,Fcancelled.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV's Good Morning
OL,13,FBritain, Ms Hudson said: "This has
OL,14,Ftaken over everything.
OL,16,F"It's been frustrating and frightening
OL,17,Fand it has really taken me back in my
OL,18,Frecovery. I've had days where I have
OL,19,Fstruggled to get out of bed.
