OL,6,F"This wouldn't have been necessary at
OL,7,Fall if things had worked properly."
OL,9,FMs Hudson had been in what she called
OL,10,Fan "incredibly difficult" relationship
OL,11,Fwith Underwood for 15 years before the
OL,12,Ffinal attack, during which he hit her
OL,13,Fwith a phone, punched her in the
OL,14,Fstomach, held a knife to her face and
OL,15,Fthreatened to killer her and himself.
OL,17,FHe slashed her arm before she managed
OL,18,Fto escape.
