OL,6,FDuring his sentencing at Sheffield
OL,7,FCrown Court he was told by a judge he
OL,8,Fposed a "significant risk" to future
OL,9,Fpartners.
OL,11,FBut last September Ms Hudson was told
OL,12,Fhe would be released by June this year.
OL,14,FIt came as the government tried to
OL,15,Fprevent the prison system collapsing
OL,16,Fby reducing the minimum an inmate must
OL,17,Fserve from 50% to 40% of their
OL,18,Fsentence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
