OL,6,FMs Hudson said she was relieved that
OL,7,FUnderwood would now remain in prison,
OL,8,Fbut worried for other victims of abuse.
OL,10,FShe said: "The bigger picture is that
OL,11,Fdomestic abusers who received lesser
OL,12,Fsentences than my abuser are still
OL,13,Fbeing released early. Victims are in
OL,14,Ffear and there is trauma around that.
OL,16,F"While I this is great for me
OL,17,Fpersonally, it doesn't solve the
OL,18,Fbigger problems with the policy.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
