OL,6,F"I'm grateful I've had the opportunity
OL,7,Fto highlight this challenge for
OL,8,Feveryone else but I would have also
OL,9,Fliked to remain in my bubble of peace
OL,10,Fand quiet and not having to relieve
OL,11,Fwhat happened to me."
OL,13,FITV News understands that the MoJ
OL,14,Finvestigated the case after Ms Hudson
OL,15,Fraised the issue and discovered that
OL,16,Fthe original court warrant omitted key
OL,17,Fdetails of Underwood's sentence.
