OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Mr Underwood is not eligible for
OL,8,Fearly release. He will remain behind
OL,9,Fbars until his standard release date.
OL,10,FWe would like to apologise to
OL,11,FElizabeth Hudson for this error.
