OL,6,F"She is right that this Government
OL,7,Finherited a prison system in crisis.
OL,8,FWe had to take difficult action to
OL,9,Fstop our prisons from collapsing and
OL,10,Fkeep our streets safe. We are now
OL,11,Ffocussed on long-term reforms,
OL,12,Fbuilding 14,000 new prison places by
OL,13,F2031 and reforming sentencing to
OL,14,Fensure our prisons never run out of
OL,15,Fspace again."
